text:
Missing comma in sentence.

http://logging.apache.org/log4j/docs/api/org/apache/log4j/Level.html

*Reads:
Defines the minimum set of levels recognized by the system, that is OFF, FATAL, 
ERROR, WARN, INFODEBUG and ALL. 

*It should read as follows:
Defines the minimum set of levels recognized by the system, that is OFF, FATAL, 
ERROR, WARN, INFO, DEBUG and ALL. 

Enhancement:
Defines the minimum set of levels recognized by the system which are OFF, 
FATAL, ERROR, WARN, INFO, DEBUG and ALL.
